title: Subnetting Secrets
description:
How to Subnet - The Easy Way

If you are sitting there wondering if there is an easy way to subnet then you have come to the right place!  Subnetting is not the mysterious skill others would have you believe.  Throw away your subnetting books, burn your subnetting course notes and learn to subnet the easy way.

Starting the program

====================



The purple Subnetting_Secrets.exe icon will launch the video player

that has been bundled with the videos.  Please DO NOT use Windows

Media Player or other brands of video player because the videos will

not run properly or have the correct controls.

Included in the torrent are Subnetting Secrets Book 1 and 2 in PDF.
